OL,5,G0535 Ainsley's Taste of the Bahamas
OL,6,     FChef Ainsley Harriott explores the
OL,7,     Fvibrant flavours, local producers,
OL,8,     Fmarkets and unique dishes of the
OL,9,     Fisland nation located in the
OL,10,     FAtlantic Ocean. He kicks off his
OL,11,     Fisland adventures with the comfort
OL,12,     Ffoods at the heart of Bahamian
OL,13,     Fcooking, from 'chicken in da bag'
OL,14,     Fat Bamboo Shack to learning to put
OL,15,     Fhis peas before his rice with chef
OL,16,     FTevin Kemp. Then he wraps things
OL,17,     Fup in his beachside kitchen with
OL,18,     Fprawn and coconut fritters served
OL,19,     Fwith a pickled coconut slaw
